Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

# IMAPAccount main
IMAPAccount icloud
Host imap.mail.me.com
PORT 993
User trajkov.ivan@icloud.com
PassCmd "pass mail"
AuthMechs LOGIN
SSLType IMAPS
SSLVersion TLSv1.2

MaildirStore icloud-local
Path ~/Mail/icloud/
Inbox ~/Mail/icloud/Inbox
SubFolders Verbatim

IMAPStore icloud-remote
Account icloud

Channel ivche
Far :icloud-remote:
Near :icloud-local:
Patterns "INBOX" "Sent" "Starred" "Trash" "Drafts" "Archive"


